data.eml:eml: A new expanded revision of the European high mountain Sciadia tenebraria species group (Lepidoptera: Geometridae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Huemer, Peter, Hausmann, Axel (2009): A new expanded revision of the European high mountain Sciadia tenebraria species group (Lepidoptera: Geometridae). Zootaxa 2117: 1-30, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.188004
